        <p>The web server sits behind the institutional firewall (red). The portal responds to client requests by using REST APIs to direct Globus cloud services (top) to operate on research data in the Science DMZ (bottom center) and/or to interact with other services (center right). Data flows reliably and securely between Globus endpoints without traversing the firewall.</p>
